text: David Hutto (born June 20, 1977) is a former American race car driver. He raced in the NASCAR Busch Series between 1996 and 1997. Before that, he won the championship in 1995 in the NASCAR Goody's Dash Series, which no longer exists. Hutto also raced in the NASCAR Southeast Series and the IPOWER Dash Series ==References== Category:American racecar drivers Category:1977 births Category:NASCAR drivers
